{"tid":1645344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"十八區！！！讓火燒得更旺盛！！！","createTime":"2019-10-11T00:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T03:49:52.000Z","uid":260414,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00bd51d2ca5654e6ab2b5103330e3eeeac0a48d4","tid":1645344,"uid":260414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:45:04.000Z","msg":"我知大家都好嬲！但好嬲還好嬲，我地要確實咁做野，先對得住犧牲左同埋比黑警侮辱既手足！唔係話唔查，但我地查之餘都要比極權知道我地團火仲係燒得好旺盛！<br />\n<br />\n雖然已經有人開左Post，但我知道好快會比風向狗搞到沉，各位手足幫手推行動post，見一個推一個呀！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4A5TaM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4A5TaM.jpg&h=93fe61a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce7a575c8cdac1a57ad76fce7fa9481fbda100d9","tid":1645344,"uid":258133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VAyOQYL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVAyOQYL.jpg&h=e02ae768&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc17007c767ad324a6527c84bf3557eb17448fe8","tid":1645344,"uid":260414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:47:40.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"cb7a2eb312606b0b805a7c510ee0634b77b59282","tid":1645344,"uid":260414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:47:50.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"69d2b91a3bfd32ae7a04fea474aef9735d119126","tid":1645344,"uid":260414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:48:06.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"886439c9e36fc3989554bf36bf055aedd487c0eb","tid":1645344,"uid":260414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:48:30.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"65ef509a462d4e212dfde276d223fccb90e8fc98","tid":1645344,"uid":260414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:48:45.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"4ea913704c8ac38e700a06363558e1ac5a0e10c3","tid":1645344,"uid":260414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci